dBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:20:45.000Z","msg":"Holiday Inn Express / Ibis / Novotel 有冇人住過？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T02:15:51.000Z","msg":"3間都住過"},{"pid":"c4c755f538fd414d91e9303e85f1a255c850c79f","tid":650523,"uid":90000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ee9433b74b3a77afd31092b5d4b847e05ec959a","tid":650523,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:20:45.000Z","msg":"Holiday Inn Express / Ibis / Novotel 有冇人住過？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T03:08:52.000Z","msg":"Novotel &gt;Holiday inn express &gt;ibis <br />\n<br />\n住過三間 Novotel sukhumvit 20, Novotel platinum, Novotel siam <br />\n<br />\nSukhumvit 20=platinum &gt;siam<br />\n<br />\nIbis好多印度人唔鐘意<br />\n<br />\nHoliday inn express 冇泳池普通訓覺都唔錯既"},{"pid":"a5dae290ab0465cfe0251211f75e5fa65bb565e6","tid":650523,"uid":36547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T11:28:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人住過以下酒店:<br />\n1. U sukhumvit <br />\n2. anantara sathorn<br />\n3. arte hotel<br />\n4. well hotel<br />\n<br />\n講下有咩好同唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1a70193bd442201a26e72b43a9f694d171779b","tid":650523,"uid":75384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T14:51:01.000Z","msg":"Hilton <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6e28ac693143603178c939039608ca2b7dd69f","tid":650523,"uid":160282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T15:00:47.000Z","msg":"marriott bangkok,有個大圓形浴缸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e30816355b74026d0f8065a74bedff551434b2","tid":650523,"uid":99183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"So Sofitel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c97494c94ced9b2662f048288cbe26e39f63dd5","tid":650523,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4e30816355b74026d0f8065a74bedff551434b2","tid":650523,"uid":99183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"So Sofitel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T15:09:54.000Z","msg":"呢間好想去住<br />\n個景好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜價錢過晒budget，地點又唔算最就腳"},{"pid":"a22b2f787cf32a2f97488dfde69a97ce5bd4a4dd","tid":650523,"uid":8246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49f651637351cd1491d18e5ea2dbec4f7f366514","tid":650523,"uid":18833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ad05ba687c842a99d97194d118eae98db4cca52","tid":650523,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:11:08.000Z","msg":"黎緊想同女友去曼谷玩下，主要都係去動物園，同飲飲食食，行下market<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地對四面佛果d景點冇乜興趣，所以就應該唔會去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n追左幾個post，見到巴打推介左好多酒店，但係選擇真係太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我要求一定要乾淨，唔要有昆蟲之類，或者浴室污糟都一定唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，價錢7百樓下，便d更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 交通盡量方便啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打住過邊間係真心覺得乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求推介俾小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T12:18:52.000Z","msg":"水門 百克里酒店唔錯 方便 對面有雞飯 酒店樓下有夜市"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T15:12:54.000Z","msg":"住過...乾淨..間房好大好新淨..<br />\n如果住記得住MAIN BUILDING, 上次住第2座出入好麻煩..<br />\n好近水門雞飯同BIG C<br />\n但係2個BTS站中間, 行去都要20分鐘"},{"pid":"b279e72bac0772a2a2d021ee6f65620494a28db2","tid":650523,"uid":23217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0e0038f4d752aaf8b4ff